title: Road.Redemption-CODEX
description:
O D E X
P R E S E N T S

Road Redemption (c)

Release Date: 10/2017 Protection: Steam
Discs: 1 Genre: Action

Road Redemption is an action racing game where you lead your
motorcycle gang on an epic journey across the country in a brutal
driving combat adventure. Earn money by completing races
assassinations, robberies, and other challenges in your path. As
you collect loot, you'll upgrade your character, your bike, and
your weapons. One Life To Live Driving a motorcycle at 100 mph
while trying to hit someone with a pipe is dangerous, and death can
come quickly
